<doc id="322565" wikidata="Q5094450" url="?curid=322565" title="Chevy, el Ponzoñú">
<text>Chevy, el Ponzoñú is a fictional Puerto Rican television character, played by Puerto Rican comedian Melwin Cedeño. He made his debut on Puerto Rican TV in 1990. He is a native of Ponce, Puerto Rico.

